    "tagline": "The art of creation put into work",
    "body": "The story of Handmade by Caci begins in 2015 when we decided to share the handmade pieces created in our free time. The skilled hands of Slavica Petrevska created many knitted products, then origami, jewelry, accessories, napkin rings, greeting cards, paper cakes and more. As time passed, creativity grew, the pieces multiplied, and Katerina also joined the work. Today Handmade by Caci consists of pieces made with much effort, love and care. Our products are unique, fully handmade from various materials and available to all. Because creativity is not a hobby but a lifestyle and a joy, we will continue to create."
